<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Flauta Doce — Módulos 6 a 10</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Baloo+2:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Nunito:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
/* ===== DESIGN TOKENS ===== */
:root{
  --cream:#FFF9F2;
  --parchment:#F2EBE0;
  --parchment2:#E8DDD0;
 
  --coral:#C8583A;
  --coral-mid:#E07050;
  --coral-lt:#FDEADF;
  --coral-dk:#7A3020;
 
  --teal:#1D8B7A;
  --teal-mid:#3DBBAA;
  --teal-lt:#DCFAF3;
  --teal-dk:#0A5044;
 
  --gold:#B07A10;
  --gold-mid:#E0A030;
  --gold-lt:#FEF6DC;
  --gold-dk:#6A4A08;
 
  --plum:#6040A0;
  --plum-mid:#8060C0;
  --plum-lt:#F0EAFF;
  --plum-dk:#382460;
 
  --rose:#A8305A;
  --rose-mid:#D05888;
  --rose-lt:#FDE8F2;
  --rose-dk:#620035;
 
  --ink:#2A1A0A;
  --ink2:#6A5A4A;
  --ink3:#A8988A;
 
  --white:#FFFFFF;
  --border:rgba(42,26,10,0.10);
  --shadow:0 4px 28px rgba(42,26,10,0.10);
  --shadow-sm:0 2px 12px rgba(42,26,10,0.08);
}
 
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{
  background:var(--cream);
  font-family:'Nunito',sans-serif;
  color:var(--ink);
  min-height:100vh;
}
 
/* ===== HEADER ===== */
.site-header{
  background:var(--ink);
  padding:22px 32px 18px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:18px;
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;
}
.site-header::before{
  content:'';position:absolute;
  right:-60px;top:-60px;
  width:240px;height:240px;border-radius:50%;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
}
.hdr-icon{
  width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;
  background:var(--coral);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  font-size:26px;flex-shrink:0;
}
.hdr-text h1{
  font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;
  font-size:22px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;
  line-height:1.1;
}
.hdr-text p{
  font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
  font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.06em;margin-top:2px;
}
.hdr-badge{
  margin-left:auto;
  background:var(--coral);color:#fff;
  font-size:12px;font-weight:800;
  padding:5px 14px;border-radius:20px;
  letter-spacing:.04em;flex-shrink:0;
}
 
/* ===== NAV ===== */
.nav{
  display:flex;overflow-x:auto;gap:3px;
  padding:10px 20px;background:var(--white);
  border-bottom:1.5px solid var(--border);
  scrollbar-width:none;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;
}
.nav::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none}
.ntab{
  flex-shrink:0;padding:8px 16px;border-radius:40px;
  border:1.5px solid transparent;
  background:transparent;cursor:pointer;
  font-family:'Nunito',sans-serif;
  font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink2);
  transition:all .18s;white-space:nowrap;
}
.ntab:hover{background:var(--parchment);color:var(--ink);}
.ntab.on{background:var(--ink);color:#fff;}
 
/* ===== CONTENT ===== */
.content{padding:28px 20px 60px;max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;}
.section{display:none;}
.section.on{display:block;animation:fadeIn .25s ease;}
@keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(6px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
 
/* ===== MODULE HEADER ===== */
.mod-header{
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;
  margin-bottom:24px;
}
.mod-num{
  width:56px;height:56px;border-radius:16px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;
  font-size:22px;font-weight:800;
  flex-shrink:0;color:#fff;
}
.mod-meta{}
.mod-tag{
  font-size:11px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.12em;
  text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:3px;
}
.mod-title{
  font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;
  font-size:26px;font-weight:800;color:var(--ink);
  line-height:1.15;
}
.mod-desc{
  font-size:14px;color:var(--ink2);line-height:1.65;
  margin-bottom:24px;
}
 
/* ===== CARD ===== */
.card{
  background:var(--white);border-radius:20px;
  border:1.5px solid var(--border);
  box-shadow:var(--shadow);
  padding:26px 24px;margin-bottom:20px;
  overflow:hidden;
}
.card h3{
  font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;
  font-size:17px;font-weight:700;
  color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:16px;
}
 
/* ===== TIP BOX ===== */
.tip{
  border-radius:14px;padding:14px 18px;
  display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;
  margin-top:16px;border:1px solid;
}
.tip.green{background:var(--teal-lt);border-color:var(--teal-mid);}
.tip.orange{background:var(--coral-lt);border-color:var(--coral-mid);}
.tip.yellow{background:var(--gold-lt);border-color:var(--gold-mid);}
.tip.purple{background:var(--plum-lt);border-color:var(--plum-mid);}
.tip-ico{font-size:20px;flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;}
.tip-txt{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink2);line-height:1.6;font-weight:600;}
.tip-txt strong{color:var(--ink);}
 
/* ===== GRID HELPERS ===== */
.g2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;}
.g3{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:14px;}
.g4{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:12px;}
@media(max-width:540px){
  .g2,.g3,.g4{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;}
  .g4{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}
}
@media(max-width:360px){
  .g2,.g3,.g4{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
}
 
/* ===== BREATH CARD ===== */
.breath-card{
  border-radius:16px;padding:20px 16px;
  text-align:center;border:2px solid;
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;
}
.breath-card h4{
  font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;
  font-size:15px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px;
}
.breath-card p{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink2);line-height:1.5;}
 
/* ===== SYLLABLE CHIPS ===== */
.chip{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;
  padding:6px 14px;border-radius:20px;
  font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;
  font-size:14px;font-weight:700;
  border:1.5px solid;margin:3px;
}
 
/* ===== FINGERING ===== */
.fing-wrap{
  border-radius:16px;padding:20px 14px 16px;
  text-align:center;border:2px solid;
}
.fing-note-name{
  font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;
  font-size:22px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:2px;
}
.fing-note-sub{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;opacity:.5;letter-spacing:.05em;margin-bottom:12px;}
 
/* ===== RHYTHM BLOCK ===== */
.rblock{
  border-radius:12px;padding:14px 10px 10px;
  text-align:center;min-width:52px;
  border:2px solid;cursor:pointer;
  transition:transform .12s,box-shadow .12s;
  user-select:none;
}
.rblock:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);}
.rblock:active{transform:scale(0.95);}
.rb-note{
  font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;
  font-size:20px;font-weight:800;line-height:1;
  margin-bottom:6px;
}
.rb-syl{
  font-size:10px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.03em;
  background:rgba(0,0,0,0.07);border-radius:5px;
  padding:2px 5px;color:var(--ink2);
}
.bar{width:2px;height:50px;background:var(--ink);opacity:.18;border-radius:2px;align-self:center;margin:0 4px;}
 
/* ===== CELL BUILDER ===== */
.cell-slot{
  width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:12px;
  border:2px dashed var(--parchment2);
  background:var(--parchment);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  cursor:pointer;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;
  color:var(--ink3);transition:all .15s;
  flex-shrink:0;
}
.cell-slot:hover{border-color:var(--coral);background:var(--coral-lt);}
.cell-slot.filled{border-style:solid;}
.cell-slot.filled.c{border-color:var(--coral);background:var(--coral-lt);}
.cell-slot.filled.t{border-color:var(--teal);background:var(--teal-lt);}
.cell-slot.filled.g{border-color:var(--gold);background:var(--gold-lt);}
.cell-slot.filled.p{border-color:var(--plum);background:var(--plum-lt);}
.cell-slot.filled.r{border-color:var(--rose);background:var(--rose-lt);}
 
/* ===== PROGRESS STEPS ===== */
.steps{display:flex;gap:0;overflow-x:auto;margin-bottom:20px;}
.step{
  flex:1;min-width:90px;
  padding:14px 10px;text-align:center;
  border-right:1.5px solid var(--border);
  position:relative;
}
.step:last-child{border-right:none;}
.step-n{
  width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:50%;
  background:var(--parchment);border:2px solid var(--parchment2);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:800;
  color:var(--ink2);margin:0 auto 8px;
  transition:all .2s;
}
.step.done .step-n{background:var(--coral);border-color:var(--coral-dk);color:#fff;}
.step-label{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink2);line-height:1.3;}
 
/* ===== INTERACTIVE BEAT ROW ===== */
.beat-pill{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:50%;
  border:2px solid var(--parchment2);
  font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:800;
  color:var(--ink2);margin:3px;
  transition:all .07s;
}
.beat-pill.hi{background:var(--coral);border-color:var(--coral-dk);color:#fff;transform:scale(1.25);}
.beat-pill.lo{background:var(--teal-lt);border-color:var(--teal);color:var(--teal-dk);}
.beat-pill.rest{background:var(--parchment);border-color:var(--parchment2);color:var(--ink3);font-style:italic;}
 
/* ===== NOTATION STAFF (simplified) ===== */
.staff-wrap{
  position:relative;margin:16px 0;
  height:80px;overflow:hidden;
}
.staff-line{
  position:absolute;left:0;right:0;height:1.5px;
  background:var(--ink2);opacity:.25;
}
 
/* ===== PROGRESS DOTS ===== */
.pdots{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:8px;padding:20px 0;}
.pdot{
  width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;
  background:var(--parchment2);cursor:pointer;
  transition:all .2s;
}
.pdot.on{background:var(--coral);width:24px;border-radius:4px;}
 
/* ===== INTERACTIVE BTN ===== */
.ibtn{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
  padding:10px 22px;border-radius:40px;
  font-family:'Nunito',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;
  border:1.5px solid;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;
}
.ibtn.coral{background:var(--coral);border-color:var(--coral-dk);color:#fff;}
.ibtn.coral:hover{background:var(--coral-dk);}
.ibtn.teal{background:var(--teal);border-color:var(--teal-dk);color:#fff;}
.ibtn.teal:hover{background:var(--teal-dk);}
.ibtn.ghost{background:transparent;border-color:var(--border);color:var(--ink2);}
.ibtn.ghost:hover{background:var(--parchment);border-color:var(--ink2);}
 
/* ===== PLAYER ===== */
.player{
  background:var(--parchment);border-radius:16px;
  padding:18px;border:1px solid var(--border);margin-top:14px;
}
.player-ctrls{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:12px;}
 
/* ===== DYNAMICS SCALE ===== */
.dyn-scale{
  display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:4px;
  height:48px;
}
.dyn-bar{
  flex:1;border-radius:4px 4px 0 0;
  transition:background .3s,height .3s;
}
 
/* ===== SONG GRID ===== */
.song-row{
  display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:4px;
  flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:14px;
}
 
/* ===== WAVEFORM ANIM ===== */
@keyframes wave{
  0%,100%{transform:scaleY(1)}
  50%{transform:scaleY(2.4)}
}
.wave-bar{
  width:4px;border-radius:2px;
  display:inline-block;background:currentColor;
  transform-origin:bottom;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
 
<!-- =============================== HEADER =============================== -->
<header class="site-header">
  <div class="hdr-icon">🎵</div>
  <div class="hdr-text">
    <h1>Flauta Doce — Método Ilustrado</h1>
    <p>Gramani · Konnakol · Fundamental 1</p>
  </div>
  <div class="hdr-badge">Módulos 6–10</div>
</header>
 
<!-- =============================== NAV =============================== -->
<nav class="nav">
  <button class="ntab on"  onclick="show(6,this)">⑥ Respiração</button>
  <button class="ntab"     onclick="show(7,this)">⑦ O Silêncio</button>
  <button class="ntab"     onclick="show(8,this)">⑧ Novas Notas</button>
  <button class="ntab"     onclick="show(9,this)">⑨ Células Rítmicas</button>
  <button class="ntab"     onclick="show(10,this)">⑩ Primeira Música</button>
</nav>
 
<div class="content">
 
<!-- ================================================================
     MÓDULO 6 — RESPIRAÇÃO E SOPRO
================================================================ -->
<div class="section on" id="sec6">
 
  <div class="mod-header">
    <div class="mod-num" style="background:var(--coral)">6</div>
    <div class="mod-meta">
      <div class="mod-tag" style="color:var(--coral)">Módulo 6 · Técnica</div>
      <div class="mod-title">A Respiração e o Sopro</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="mod-desc">Gramani ensinava que o corpo todo é instrumento. A respiração é o motor da flauta — ela define dinâmica, fraseado e até o ritmo! O Konnakol usa a mesma energia do sopro na voz.</p>
 
  <!-- Diagrama respiração -->
  <div class="card">
    <h3>🫁 Como Respirar para Tocar</h3>
    <svg viewBox="0 0 680 260" width="100%">
      <!-- Silhouette torso -->
      <ellipse cx="340" cy="90" rx="58" ry="68" fill="#F2A07E" opacity=".22"/>
      <!-- Head -->
      <ellipse cx="340" cy="30" rx="28" ry="28" fill="#F2A07E" opacity=".35"/>
      <!-- Neck -->
      <rect x="326" y="54" width="28" height="20" rx="8" fill="#F2A07E" opacity=".3"/>
      <!-- Lungs left -->
      <path d="M282 100 Q262 80 268 120 Q272 148 296 158 L310 148 Q295 128 297 108 Z" fill="#C8583A" opacity=".22" stroke="#C8583A" stroke-width="1" fill-rule="evenodd"/>
      <!-- Lungs right -->
      <path d="M398 100 Q418 80 412 120 Q408 148 384 158 L370 148 Q385 128 383 108 Z" fill="#C8583A" opacity=".22" stroke="#C8583A" stroke-width="1"/>
      <!-- Trachea -->
      <rect x="330" y="70" width="20" height="38" rx="8" fill="#C8583A" opacity=".3"/>
      <!-- Diaphragm -->
      <path d="M270 165 Q340 185 410 165" fill="none" stroke="#1D8B7A" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" id="diaphragm"/>
      <!-- Arrows inhale -->
      <g opacity=".8">
        <path d="M240 70 L270 90" stroke="#1D8B7A" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" marker-end="url(#arr-teal)" fill="none"/>
        <path d="M440 70 L410 90" stroke="#1D8B7A" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" marker-end="url(#arr-teal)" fill="none"/>
        <text x="215" y="68" font-family="Baloo 2,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#1D8B7A">ar entra</text>
        <text x="412" y="68" font-family="Baloo 2,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#1D8B7A">ar entra</text>
      </g>
      <!-- Diaphragm label -->
      <line x1="340" y1="176" x2="340" y2="210" stroke="#1D8B7A" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3 3"/>
      <text x="340" y="224" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#1D8B7A">Diafragma — sobe e desce!</text>
 
      <!-- Markers -->
      <defs>
        <marker id="arr-teal" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="8" refY="5" markerWidth="5" markerHeight="5" orient="auto">
          <path d="M2 2L8 5L2 8" fill="none" stroke="#1D8B7A" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </marker>
        <marker id="arr-coral" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="8" refY="5" markerWidth="5" markerHeight="5" orient="auto">
          <path d="M2 2L8 5L2 8" fill="none" stroke="#C8583A" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </marker>
      </defs>
 
      <!-- Flute and breath arrow -->
      <rect x="470" y="118" width="180" height="14" rx="7" fill="#B07A10" opacity=".45"/>
      <rect x="466" y="112" width="22" height="26" rx="8" fill="#B07A10" opacity=".55"/>
      <path d="M400 125 L464 125" stroke="#C8583A" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" marker-end="url(#arr-coral)" fill="none"/>
      <text x="428" y="116" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Baloo 2,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#C8583A">sopro</text>
 
      <!-- Right side labels -->
      <text x="530" y="108" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Baloo 2,sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="#6A4A08">Flauta Doce</text>
 
      <!-- 3 breath types -->
      <rect x="20" y="205" width="195" height="46" rx="12" fill="#DCF3EE" stroke="#1D8B7A" stroke-width="1"/>
      <text x="117" y="222" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Baloo 2,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#0A5044">Inspire pelo nariz</text>
      <text x="117" y="240" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="600" fill="#3DBBAA">barriga para fora ↓</text>
 
      <rect x="242" y="205" width="195" height="46" rx="12" fill="#FDEADF" stroke="#C8583A" stroke-width="1"/>
      <text x="339" y="222" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Baloo 2,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#7A3020">Sopre pela boca</text>
      <text x="339" y="240" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="600" fill="#C8583A">barriga para dentro ↑</text>
 
      <rect x="464" y="205" width="195" height="46" rx="12" fill="#FEF6DC" stroke="#B07A10" stroke-width="1"/>
      <text x="561" y="222" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Baloo 2,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#6A4A08">Apoie no diafragma</text>
      <text x="561" y="240" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="600" fill="#B07A10">controle a coluna de ar</text>
    </svg>
  </div>
 
  <!-- Dinâmicas -->
  <div class="card">
    <h3>📢 Dinâmicas: Forte e Piano com Sopro</h3>
    <div class="g2">
      <div style="border-radius:16px;padding:20px;background:var(--coral-lt);border:2px solid var(--coral)">
        <div style="font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;font-size:32px;font-weight:800;color:var(--coral);margin-bottom:8px;">f</div>
        <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--coral-dk);margin-bottom:6px;">Forte — sopro cheio</div>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:3px;height:36px;">
          <div style="flex:1;border-radius:3px 3px 0 0;height:60%;background:var(--coral);opacity:.4;"></div>
          <div style="flex:1;border-radius:3px 3px 0 0;height:70%;background:var(--coral);opacity:.5;"></div>
          <div style="flex:1;border-radius:3px 3px 0 0;height:85%;background:var(--coral);opacity:.7;"></div>
          <div style="flex:1;border-radius:3px 3px 0 0;height:95%;background:var(--coral);opacity:.9;"></div>
          <div style="flex:1;border-radius:3px 3px 0 0;height:100%;background:var(--coral);"></div>
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--ink3);margin-top:8px;font-weight:600;">Gramani: "FORTE" = peso no tempo</div>
      </div>
      <div style="border-radius:16px;padding:20px;background:var(--teal-lt);border:2px solid var(--teal)">
        <div style="font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;font-size:32px;font-weight:800;color:var(--teal);margin-bottom:8px;">p</div>
        <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--teal-dk);margin-bottom:6px;">Piano — sopro suave</div>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:3px;height:36px;">
          <div style="flex:1;border-radius:3px 3px 0 0;height:100%;background:var(--teal);"></div>
          <div style="flex:1;border-radius:3px 3px 0 0;height:80%;background:var(--teal);opacity:.7;"></div>
          <div style="flex:1;border-radius:3px 3px 0 0;height:55%;background:var(--teal);opacity:.5;"></div>
          <div style="flex:1;border-radius:3px 3px 0 0;height:35%;background:var(--teal);opacity:.35;"></div>
          <div style="flex:1;border-radius:3px 3px 0 0;height:20%;background:var(--teal);opacity:.2;"></div>
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--ink3);margin-top:8px;font-weight:600;">Konnakol: "ta" minúsculo = leve</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tip orange" style="margin-top:16px;">
      <span class="tip-ico">🕯️</span>
      <p class="tip-txt"><strong>Exercício da vela:</strong> Coloque uma vela acesa a 30 cm. Sopre sem apagá-la — esse é o sopro certo para a flauta! Forte demais = apaga. Fraco demais = não vibra.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
 
  <!-- Konnakol + sopro -->
  <div class="card">
    <h3>🎤 Konnakol Vocal: a Voz como Sopro</h3>
    <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--ink2);margin-bottom:16px;line-height:1.6;">No Konnakol, as sílabas têm dinâmica própria. <b>Ta</b> forte = tempo forte. <b>ka / ki / di / mi</b> = mais leve. A mesma lei vale no sopro!</p>
    <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;margin-bottom:14px;">
      <div style="background:var(--coral-lt);border:2px solid var(--coral);border-radius:14px;padding:14px 18px;text-align:center;min-width:100px;">
        <div style="font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:800;color:var(--coral);">Ta</div>
        <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--coral-dk);margin-top:4px;">FORTE · f</div>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--teal-lt);border:2px solid var(--teal);border-radius:14px;padding:14px 18px;text-align:center;min-width:100px;opacity:.85">
        <div style="font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:var(--teal);">Ka</div>
        <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--teal-dk);margin-top:4px;">médio · mf</div>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--gold-lt);border:2px solid var(--gold);border-radius:14px;padding:14px 18px;text-align:center;min-width:100px;opacity:.75">
        <div style="font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;font-size:20px;font-weight:600;color:var(--gold);">Ki</div>
        <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gold-dk);margin-top:4px;">suave · mp</div>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--plum-lt);border:2px solid var(--plum);border-radius:14px;padding:14px 18px;text-align:center;min-width:100px;opacity:.65">
        <div style="font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:500;color:var(--plum);">Di</div>
        <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--plum-dk);margin-top:4px;">leve · p</div>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--rose-lt);border:2px solid var(--rose);border-radius:14px;padding:14px 18px;text-align:center;min-width:100px;opacity:.55">
        <div style="font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:500;color:var(--rose);">Mi</div>
        <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--rose-dk);margin-top:4px;">muito leve · pp</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tip green">
      <span class="tip-ico">💡</span>
      <p class="tip-txt"><strong>Gramani ensina:</strong> A hierarquia do pulso é a hierarquia da dinâmica. O primeiro tempo é sempre mais "pesado" — isso vale para a voz E para o sopro da flauta.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
 
<!-- ================================================================
     MÓDULO 7 — O SILÊNCIO TAMBÉM É MÚSICA
================================================================ -->
<div class="section" id="sec7">
 
  <div class="mod-header">
    <div class="mod-num" style="background:var(--plum)">7</div>
    <div class="mod-meta">
      <div class="mod-tag" style="color:var(--plum)">Módulo 7 · Ritmo</div>
      <div class="mod-title">O Silêncio Também é Música</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="mod-desc">Para Gramani, a pausa não é "nada" — ela é um tempo cheio de tensão e expectativa. No Konnakol, o silêncio tem nome: "shh" ou simplesmente a ausência de sílaba, mas o pulso continua!</p>
 
  <!-- O que é pausa -->
  <div class="card">
    <h3>🤫 O que é uma Pausa?</h3>
    <svg viewBox="0 0 680 160" width="100%">
      <!-- Timeline bar -->
      <rect x="30" y="70" width="620" height="4" rx="2" fill="#E8DDD0"/>
      <!-- Pulse marks -->
      <line x1="30"  y1="58" x2="30"  y2="82" stroke="#2A1A0A" stroke-width="2" opacity=".3"/>
      <line x1="185" y1="58" x2="185" y2="82" stroke="#2A1A0A" stroke-width="2" opacity=".3"/>
      <line x1="340" y1="58" x2="340" y2="82" stroke="#2A1A0A" stroke-width="2" opacity=".3"/>
      <line x1="495" y1="58" x2="495" y2="82" stroke="#2A1A0A" stroke-width="2" opacity=".3"/>
      <line x1="650" y1="58" x2="650" y2="82" stroke="#2A1A0A" stroke-width="2" opacity=".3"/>
      <!-- Notes (sound) -->
      <rect x="30"  y="40" width="145" height="28" rx="8" fill="#C8583A"/>
      <text x="102" y="59" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Baloo 2,sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="white">♩ nota</text>
      <!-- Rest (silence) -->
      <rect x="185" y="40" width="145" height="28" rx="8" fill="#F0EAFF" stroke="#6040A0" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="5 3"/>
      <text x="257" y="59" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Baloo 2,sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="#6040A0">𝄽 pausa</text>
      <!-- Note -->
      <rect x="340" y="40" width="145" height="28" rx="8" fill="#1D8B7A"/>
      <text x="412" y="59" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Baloo 2,sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="white">♩ nota</text>
      <!-- Note -->
      <rect x="495" y="40" width="145" height="28" rx="8" fill="#C8583A"/>
      <text x="567" y="59" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Baloo 2,sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="white">♩ nota</text>
 
      <!-- Bottom labels -->
      <text x="102"  y="108" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="700" fill="#A8988A">1 pulso · SOM</text>
      <text x="257"  y="108" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="700" fill="#6040A0">1 pulso · SILÊNCIO</text>
      <text x="412"  y="108" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="700" fill="#A8988A">1 pulso · SOM</text>
      <text x="567"  y="108" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="700" fill="#A8988A">1 pulso · SOM</text>
 
      <!-- "Pulso continua" arrow -->
      <path d="M30 130 L650 130" stroke="#2A1A0A" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3" opacity=".2" fill="none"/>
      <text x="340" y="148" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="800" fill="#A8988A">O PULSO NUNCA PARA — mesmo no silêncio!</text>
    </svg>
    <div class="tip purple">
      <span class="tip-ico">🫀</span>
      <p class="tip-txt"><strong>Gramani dizia:</strong> "A pausa é uma nota que não soa." Bata o pé no silêncio também. O coração não para — o ritmo também não.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
 
  <!-- Símbolos das pausas -->
  <div class="card">
    <h3>📝 Os Símbolos das Pausas</h3>
    <div class="g3">
      <div style="border-radius:16px;padding:20px;text-align:center;background:var(--parchment);border:1.5px solid var(--border);">
        <div style="font-size:42px;line-height:1;margin-bottom:8px;color:var(--ink);">𝄻</div>
        <div style="font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);">Pausa Inteira</div>
        <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink3);margin-top:4px;">4 pulsos de silêncio</div>
        <div style="margin-top:8px;background:var(--plum-lt);border-radius:8px;padding:5px;font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--plum);">shh shh shh shh</div>
      </div>
      <div style="border-radius:16px;padding:20px;text-align:center;background:var(--parchment);border:1.5px solid var(--border);">
        <div style="font-size:42px;line-height:1;margin-bottom:8px;color:var(--ink);">𝄼</div>
        <div style="font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);">Pausa Metade</div>
        <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink3);margin-top:4px;">2 pulsos de silêncio</div>
        <div style="margin-top:8px;background:var(--plum-lt);border-radius:8px;padding:5px;font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--plum);">shh shh</div>
      </div>
      <div style="border-radius:16px;padding:20px;text-align:center;background:var(--parchment);border:1.5px solid var(--border);">
        <div style="font-size:42px;line-height:1;margin-bottom:8px;color:var(--ink);">𝄽</div>
        <div style="font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);">Pausa Quarto</div>
        <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink3);margin-top:4px;">1 pulso de silêncio</div>
        <div style="margin-top:8px;background:var(--plum-lt);border-radius:8px;padding:5px;font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--plum);">shh</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
 
  <!-- Exercício com pausas -->
  <div class="card">
    <h3>🎮 Exercício: Toque e Silencie!</h3>
    <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--ink2);margin-bottom:14px;">Nos blocos <span style="background:var(--plum-lt);border:1px solid var(--plum);border-radius:6px;padding:2px 8px;font-weight:700;color:var(--plum);font-size:12px;">shh</span> — levante a língua da boquilha e silencie, mas continue sentindo o pulso!</p>
 
    <div id="pause-ex" style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;margin-bottom:16px;"></div>
 
    <div class="player">
      <div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink3);letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:10px;">Padrão de Exercício</div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap;" id="pause-pattern"></div>
      <div class="player-ctrls">
        <button class="ibtn coral" onclick="togglePausePlayer()">
          <span id="pause-play-ico">▶</span> <span id="pause-play-txt">Iniciar</span>
        </button>
        <button class="ibtn ghost" onclick="setPauseEx(0)">Padrão 1</button>
        <button class="ibtn ghost" onclick="setPauseEx(1)">Padrão 2</button>
        <button class="ibtn ghost" onclick="setPauseEx(2)">Padrão 3</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
 
<!-- ================================================================
     MÓDULO 8 — NOVAS NOTAS: RÉ, MI E FÁ
================================================================ -->
<div class="section" id="sec8">
 
  <div class="mod-header">
    <div class="mod-num" style="background:var(--gold)">8</div>
    <div class="mod-meta">
      <div class="mod-tag" style="color:var(--gold)">Módulo 8 · Dedilhados</div>
      <div class="mod-title">Novas Notas: Ré, Mi e Fá</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="mod-desc">Agora que você conhece Si, Lá e Sol, vamos aprender três novas notas que completam a escala de Ré até Si! Com elas, você consegue tocar dezenas de músicas.</p>
 
  <!-- Escala visual -->
  <div class="card">
    <h3>🎼 A Escala Completa — Do Grave ao Agudo</h3>
    <svg viewBox="0 0 680 130" width="100%">
      <!-- Staff lines -->
      <line x1="30" y1="50" x2="650" y2="50" stroke="#2A1A0A" stroke-width="0.8" opacity=".2"/>
      <line x1="30" y1="66" x2="650" y2="66" stroke="#2A1A0A" stroke-width="0.8" opacity=".2"/>
      <line x1="30" y1="82" x2="650" y2="82" stroke="#2A1A0A" stroke-width="0.8" opacity=".2"/>
      <line x1="30" y1="98" x2="650" y2="98" stroke="#2A1A0A" stroke-width="0.8" opacity=".2"/>
      <line x1="30" y1="114" x2="650" y2="114" stroke="#2A1A0A" stroke-width="0.8" opacity=".2"/>
 
      <!-- Notes on staff (simplified) — Ré, Mi, Fá, Sol, Lá, Si -->
      <!-- Ré = below staff, needs ledger line -->
      <line x1="62" y1="130" x2="82" y2="130" stroke="#2A1A0A" stroke-width="1" opacity=".4"/>
      <ellipse cx="72" cy="130" rx="10" ry="7" fill="#B07A10"/>
      <text x="72" y="120" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Baloo 2,sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="800" fill="#B07A10">Ré</text>
 
      <!-- Mi = on last line -->
      <ellipse cx="162" cy="114" rx="10" ry="7" fill="#6040A0"/>
      <text x="162" y="104" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Baloo 2,sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="800" fill="#6040A0">Mi</text>
 
      <!-- Fá = first space -->
      <ellipse cx="252" cy="106" rx="10" ry="7" fill="#A8305A"/>
      <text x="252" y="96" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Baloo 2,sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="800" fill="#A8305A">Fá</text>
 
      <!-- Sol = second line -->
      <ellipse cx="342" cy="98" rx="10" ry="7" fill="#B07A10"/>
      <rect x="352" y="60" width="1.5" height="38" fill="#B07A10"/>
      <text x="342" y="90" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Baloo 2,sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="800" fill="#B07A10">Sol</text>
 
      <!-- Lá = second space -->
      <ellipse cx="432" cy="90" rx="10" ry="7" fill="#1D8B7A"/>
      <rect x="442" y="52" width="1.5" height="38" fill="#1D8B7A"/>
      <text x="432" y="82" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Baloo 2,sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="800" fill="#1D8B7A">Lá</text>
 
      <!-- Si = third line -->
      <ellipse cx="522" cy="82" rx="10" ry="7" fill="#C8583A"/>
      <rect x="532" y="44" width="1.5" height="38" fill="#C8583A"/>
      <text x="522" y="74" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Baloo 2,sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="800" fill="#C8583A">Si</text>
 
      <!-- Dó = third space NEW -->
      <ellipse cx="612" cy="74" rx="10" ry="7" fill="#A8988A" opacity=".5"/>
      <rect x="622" y="36" width="1.5" height="38" fill="#A8988A" opacity=".5"/>
      <text x="612" y="65" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Baloo 2,sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="700" fill="#A8988A">Dó*</text>
 
      <!-- NEW badges -->
      <rect x="130" y="14" width="34" height="16" rx="8" fill="#6040A0"/>
      <text x="147" y="26" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="10" font-weight="800" fill="white">NOVO</text>
      <rect x="220" y="14" width="34" height="16" rx="8" fill="#A8305A"/>
      <text x="237" y="26" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="10" font-weight="800" fill="white">NOVO</text>
      <rect x="40" y="14" width="34" height="16" rx="8" fill="#B07A10"/>
      <text x="57" y="26" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="10" font-weight="800" fill="white">NOVO</text>
 
      <!-- Arrow = ascending -->
      <text x="16" y="128" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="10" font-weight="700" fill="#A8988A">grave</text>
      <text x="660" y="75" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="10" font-weight="700" fill="#A8988A">agudo</text>
    </svg>
  </div>
 
  <!-- Dedilhados novos -->
  <div class="card">
    <h3>🖐️ Dedilhados das Novas Notas</h3>
    <div class="g3">
 
      <!-- RÉ -->
      <div class="fing-wrap" style="border-color:var(--gold);background:var(--gold-lt);">
        <div class="fing-note-name" style="color:var(--gold);">Ré</div>
        <div class="fing-note-sub">D · nota 2 · grave</div>
        <svg width="72" height="160" viewBox="0 0 72 160" style="margin:0 auto 10px;display:block;">
          <rect x="29" y="4" width="14" height="148" rx="7" fill="var(--gold-lt)" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <!-- Thumb -->
          <circle cx="36" cy="20" r="7" fill="var(--gold)" opacity=".8"/>
          <!-- Ind. esq -->
          <circle cx="36" cy="42" r="7" fill="var(--gold)"/>
          <!-- Med. esq -->
          <circle cx="36" cy="66" r="7" fill="var(--gold)"/>
          <!-- Anel esq -->
          <circle cx="36" cy="90" r="7" fill="var(--gold)"/>
          <!-- Min. esq -->
          <circle cx="36" cy="110" r="6" fill="var(--gold)"/>
          <!-- Ind. dir -->
          <circle cx="36" cy="124" r="6" fill="var(--gold)"/>
          <!-- Med. dir (half) -->
          <circle cx="36" cy="136" r="5" fill="var(--gold)"/>
          <!-- Anel dir -->
          <circle cx="36" cy="147" r="4" fill="var(--gold)"/>
        </svg>
        <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gold-dk);line-height:1.4;">Todos os dedos + polegar</div>
      </div>
 
      <!-- MI -->
      <div class="fing-wrap" style="border-color:var(--plum);background:var(--plum-lt);">
        <div class="fing-note-name" style="color:var(--plum);">Mi</div>
        <div class="fing-note-sub">E · nota 3</div>
        <svg width="72" height="160" viewBox="0 0 72 160" style="margin:0 auto 10px;display:block;">
          <rect x="29" y="4" width="14" height="148" rx="7" fill="var(--plum-lt)" stroke="var(--plum)" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <circle cx="36" cy="20" r="7" fill="var(--plum)" opacity=".8"/>
          <circle cx="36" cy="42" r="7" fill="var(--plum)"/>
          <circle cx="36" cy="66" r="7" fill="var(--plum)"/>
          <circle cx="36" cy="90" r="7" fill="var(--plum)"/>
          <circle cx="36" cy="110" r="6" fill="var(--plum)"/>
          <circle cx="36" cy="124" r="6" fill="var(--plum)"/>
          <circle cx="36" cy="136" r="5" fill="white" stroke="var(--plum)" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <circle cx="36" cy="147" r="4" fill="white" stroke="var(--plum)" stroke-width="1"/>
        </svg>
        <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--plum-dk);line-height:1.4;">Todos esq. + Ind./Med. dir.</div>
      </div>
 
      <!-- FÁ -->
      <div class="fing-wrap" style="border-color:var(--rose);background:var(--rose-lt);">
        <div class="fing-note-name" style="color:var(--rose);">Fá</div>
        <div class="fing-note-sub">F · nota 4</div>
        <svg width="72" height="160" viewBox="0 0 72 160" style="margin:0 auto 10px;display:block;">
          <rect x="29" y="4" width="14" height="148" rx="7" fill="var(--rose-lt)" stroke="var(--rose)" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <circle cx="36" cy="20" r="7" fill="var(--rose)" opacity=".8"/>
          <circle cx="36" cy="42" r="7" fill="var(--rose)"/>
          <circle cx="36" cy="66" r="7" fill="var(--rose)"/>
          <circle cx="36" cy="90" r="7" fill="var(--rose)"/>
          <circle cx="36" cy="110" r="6" fill="var(--rose)"/>
          <circle cx="36" cy="124" r="6" fill="var(--rose)"/>
          <circle cx="36" cy="136" r="5" fill="var(--rose)"/>
          <circle cx="36" cy="147" r="4" fill="white" stroke="var(--rose)" stroke-width="1"/>
        </svg>
        <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--rose-dk);line-height:1.4;">Quase tudo! Só Min. dir. abre</div>
      </div>
    </div>
 
    <div style="margin-top:16px;background:var(--parchment);border-radius:14px;padding:14px 16px;">
      <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:800;color:var(--ink3);letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px;">Legenda dos dedilhados</div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="7" fill="#C8583A"/></svg>
          <span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink2);">círculo cheio = furo fechado</span>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="6.5" fill="white" stroke="#C8583A" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
          <span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink2);">círculo vazio = furo aberto</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
 
  <!-- Escalas exercício -->
  <div class="card">
    <h3>🎵 Exercício de Escala com Konnakol</h3>
    <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--ink2);margin-bottom:14px;">Suba e desça a escala falando "Ta" para cada nota. Ré→Mi→Fá→Sol→Lá→Si e volte!</p>
    <div style="overflow-x:auto;padding-bottom:8px;">
      <div style="display:flex;gap:4px;align-items:flex-end;min-width:440px;">
        <div class="rblock" style="border-color:var(--gold);background:var(--gold-lt);">
          <div class="rb-note" style="color:var(--gold);">Ré</div>
          <div class="rb-syl">Ta</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rblock" style="border-color:var(--plum);background:var(--plum-lt);">
          <div class="rb-note" style="color:var(--plum);">Mi</div>
          <div class="rb-syl">Ta</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rblock" style="border-color:var(--rose);background:var(--rose-lt);">
          <div class="rb-note" style="color:var(--rose);">Fá</div>
          <div class="rb-syl">Ta</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rblock" style="border-color:var(--gold);background:var(--gold-lt);">
          <div class="rb-note" style="color:var(--gold);">Sol</div>
          <div class="rb-syl">Ta</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rblock" style="border-color:var(--teal);background:var(--teal-lt);">
          <div class="rb-note" style="color:var(--teal);">Lá</div>
          <div class="rb-syl">Ta</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rblock" style="border-color:var(--coral);background:var(--coral-lt);">
          <div class="rb-note" style="color:var(--coral);">Si</div>
          <div class="rb-syl">Ta</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bar"></div>
        <div class="rblock" style="border-color:var(--coral);background:var(--coral-lt);">
          <div class="rb-note" style="color:var(--coral);">Si</div>
          <div class="rb-syl">Ta</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rblock" style="border-color:var(--teal);background:var(--teal-lt);">
          <div class="rb-note" style="color:var(--teal);">Lá</div>
          <div class="rb-syl">Ta</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rblock" style="border-color:var(--gold);background:var(--gold-lt);">
          <div class="rb-note" style="color:var(--gold);">Sol</div>
          <div class="rb-syl">Ta</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rblock" style="border-color:var(--rose);background:var(--rose-lt);">
          <div class="rb-note" style="color:var(--rose);">Fá</div>
          <div class="rb-syl">Ta</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rblock" style="border-color:var(--plum);background:var(--plum-lt);">
          <div class="rb-note" style="color:var(--plum);">Mi</div>
          <div class="rb-syl">Ta</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rblock" style="border-color:var(--gold);background:var(--gold-lt);">
          <div class="rb-note" style="color:var(--gold);">Ré</div>
          <div class="rb-syl">Ta</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tip yellow" style="margin-top:14px;">
      <span class="tip-ico">🐢</span>
      <p class="tip-txt"><strong>Comece devagar!</strong> Gramani ensinava a dominar o gesto antes da velocidade. Toque a escala em 60 bpm, depois 80, depois 100. A qualidade vem antes da rapidez.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
 
<!-- ================================================================
     MÓDULO 9 — CÉLULAS RÍTMICAS
================================================================ -->
<div class="section" id="sec9">
 
  <div class="mod-header">
    <div class="mod-num" style="background:var(--teal)">9</div>
    <div class="mod-meta">
      <div class="mod-tag" style="color:var(--teal)">Módulo 9 · Composição</div>
      <div class="mod-title">Células Rítmicas — Construa seu Ritmo!</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="mod-desc">José Gramani chamava de "células rítmicas" as pequenas unidades que se repetem e constroem a música. O Konnakol usa exatamente isso: você combina Ta, Ta-Ka, Ta-Ki-Ta para criar qualquer ritmo!</p>
 
  <!-- O que é célula -->
  <div class="card">
    <h3>🧬 O que é uma Célula Rítmica?</h3>
    <svg viewBox="0 0 680 180" width="100%">
      <!-- Cell metaphor: small units building into a phrase -->
      <!-- Unit 1: Ta -->
      <rect x="20" y="30" width="80" height="60" rx="14" fill="#FDEADF" stroke="#C8583A" stroke-width="2"/>
      <text x="60" y="55" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Baloo 2,sans-serif" font-size="22" font-weight="800" fill="#C8583A">Ta</text>
      <text x="60" y="75" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="700" fill="#7A3020">1 pulso</text>
 
      <!-- + -->
      <text x="118" y="65" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Baloo 2,sans-serif" font-size="20" font-weight="800" fill="#A8988A">+</text>
 
      <!-- Unit 2: Ta Ka -->
      <rect x="134" y="30" width="120" height="60" rx="14" fill="#DCF3EE" stroke="#1D8B7A" stroke-width="2"/>
      <text x="194" y="55" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Baloo 2,sans-serif" font-size="18" font-weight="800" fill="#1D8B7A">Ta Ka</text>
      <text x="194" y="75" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="700" fill="#0A5044">2 sub-tempos</text>
 
      <!-- + -->
      <text x="272" y="65" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Baloo 2,sans-serif" font-size="20" font-weight="800" fill="#A8988A">+</text>
 
      <!-- Unit 3: Ta Ki Ta -->
      <rect x="288" y="30" width="150" height="60" rx="14" fill="#FEF6DC" stroke="#B07A10" stroke-width="2"/>
      <text x="363" y="55" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Baloo 2,sans-serif" font-size="16" font-weight="800" fill="#B07A10">Ta Ki Ta</text>
      <text x="363" y="75" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="700" fill="#6A4A08">3 sub-tempos</text>
 
      <!-- = -->
      <text x="456" y="65" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Baloo 2,sans-serif" font-size="20" font-weight="800" fill="#A8988A">=</text>
 
      <!-- Result: frase -->
      <rect x="472" y="20" width="190" height="80" rx="16" fill="var(--ink)" />
      <text x="567" y="52" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Baloo 2,sans-serif" font-size="15" font-weight="800" fill="white">Uma frase musical!</text>
      <text x="567" y="72" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.6)">4 pulsos · 1 compasso</text>
 
      <!-- Bottom: bracket -->
      <path d="M20 108 L20 120 L662 120 L662 108" fill="none" stroke="#A8988A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      <text x="340" y="140" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="800" fill="#A8988A">1 compasso = combinação de células</text>
 
      <!-- Gramani connection -->
      <rect x="160" y="152" width="360" height="22" rx="8" fill="#F0EAFF" stroke="#6040A0" stroke-width="1"/>
      <text x="340" y="167" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#6040A0">Gramani: cada célula tem seu "peso" — grave, médio ou leve</text>
    </svg>
  </div>
 
  <!-- Construtor de células -->
  <div class="card">
    <h3>🔨 Construtor de Célula — Monte o Seu Ritmo!</h3>
    <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--ink2);margin-bottom:14px;">Clique nas sílabas para adicionar ao compasso. Depois toque para ouvir!</p>
 
    <!-- Palette -->
    <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:16px;">
      <button class="ibtn" style="background:var(--coral-lt);border-color:var(--coral);color:var(--coral-dk);font-size:15px;font-weight:800;" onclick="addCell('Ta','coral')">Ta</button>
      <button class="ibtn" style="background:var(--teal-lt);border-color:var(--teal);color:var(--teal-dk);font-size:15px;font-weight:800;" onclick="addCell('Ka','teal')">Ka</button>
      <button class="ibtn" style="background:var(--gold-lt);border-color:var(--gold);color:var(--gold-dk);font-size:15px;font-weight:800;" onclick="addCell('Ki','gold')">Ki</button>
      <button class="ibtn" style="background:var(--plum-lt);border-color:var(--plum);color:var(--plum-dk);font-size:15px;font-weight:800;" onclick="addCell('Di','purple')">Di</button>
      <button class="ibtn" style="background:var(--rose-lt);border-color:var(--rose);color:var(--rose-dk);font-size:15px;font-weight:800;" onclick="addCell('Mi','rose')">Mi</button>
      <button class="ibtn" style="background:var(--parchment);border-color:var(--parchment2);color:var(--ink3);font-size:15px;font-style:italic;" onclick="addCell('shh','rest')">shh</button>
      <button class="ibtn ghost" onclick="clearCells()" style="margin-left:auto;">✕ Limpar</button>
    </div>
 
    <!-- Cell slots -->
    <div style="display:flex;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap;min-height:60px;background:var(--parchment);border-radius:14px;padding:10px;margin-bottom:14px;border:1.5px dashed var(--parchment2);" id="cell-slots">
      <span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink3);align-self:center;">↑ adicione sílabas acima</span>
    </div>
 
    <!-- Count bar -->
    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:12px;">
      <span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink3);">Sílabas:</span>
      <span style="font-size:16px;font-weight:800;color:var(--ink);" id="cell-count">0</span>
      <span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink3);">/ 8 máx.</span>
      <div style="flex:1;height:6px;background:var(--parchment2);border-radius:3px;overflow:hidden;">
        <div style="height:100%;background:var(--coral);border-radius:3px;transition:width .2s;" id="cell-bar"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
 
    <div class="player-ctrls">
      <button class="ibtn teal" onclick="playCells()">▶ Tocar Células</button>
      <button class="ibtn ghost" onclick="loadPreset(0)">Preset: Samba</button>
      <button class="ibtn ghost" onclick="loadPreset(1)">Preset: Baião</button>
      <button class="ibtn ghost" onclick="loadPreset(2)">Preset: Valsa</button>
    </div>
  </div>
 
  <!-- Padrões prontos -->
  <div class="card">
    <h3>🌟 Padrões Rítmicos Prontos para Aprender</h3>
    <div class="g2">
      <div style="border-radius:16px;padding:18px;background:var(--coral-lt);border:2px solid var(--coral);">
        <div style="font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:var(--coral);margin-bottom:10px;">Binário simples</div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:4px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px;">
          <span class="chip" style="background:var(--coral);border-color:var(--coral-dk);color:white;">Ta</span>
          <span class="chip" style="background:var(--coral-lt);border-color:var(--coral);color:var(--coral-dk);">Ka</span>
          <span class="chip" style="background:var(--coral);border-color:var(--coral-dk);color:white;">Ta</span>
          <span class="chip" style="background:var(--coral-lt);border-color:var(--coral);color:var(--coral-dk);">Ka</span>
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--coral-dk);">Gramani: 1-e-2-e · 2/4</div>
      </div>
      <div style="border-radius:16px;padding:18px;background:var(--teal-lt);border:2px solid var(--teal);">
        <div style="font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:var(--teal);margin-bottom:10px;">Ternário simples</div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:4px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px;">
          <span class="chip" style="background:var(--teal);border-color:var(--teal-dk);color:white;">Ta</span>
          <span class="chip" style="background:var(--teal-lt);border-color:var(--teal);color:var(--teal-dk);">Ki</span>
          <span class="chip" style="background:var(--teal-lt);border-color:var(--teal);color:var(--teal-dk);">Ta</span>
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--teal-dk);">Gramani: 1-2-3 · 3/4</div>
      </div>
      <div style="border-radius:16px;padding:18px;background:var(--gold-lt);border:2px solid var(--gold);">
        <div style="font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:10px;">Com pausa</div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:4px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px;">
          <span class="chip" style="background:var(--gold);border-color:var(--gold-dk);color:white;">Ta</span>
          <span class="chip" style="background:var(--gold-lt);border-color:var(--gold);color:var(--gold-dk);">Ka</span>
          <span class="chip" style="background:var(--parchment);border-color:var(--parchment2);color:var(--ink3);font-style:italic;">shh</span>
          <span class="chip" style="background:var(--gold);border-color:var(--gold-dk);color:white;">Ta</span>
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gold-dk);">Gramani: 1-e-_-2 · síncopa!</div>
      </div>
      <div style="border-radius:16px;padding:18px;background:var(--plum-lt);border:2px solid var(--plum);">
        <div style="font-family:'Baloo 2',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:var(--plum);margin-bottom:10px;">Quaternário</div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:4px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px;">
          <span class="chip" style="background:var(--plum);border-color:var(--plum-dk);color:white;">Ta</span>
          <span class="chip" style="background:var(--plum-lt);border-color:var(--plum);color:var(--plum-dk);">Ka</span>
          <span class="chip" style="background:var(--plum-lt);border-color:var(--plum);color:var(--plum-dk);">Di</span>
          <span class="chip" style="background:var(--plum-lt);border-color:var(--plum);color:var(--plum-dk);">Mi</span>
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--plum-dk);">Gramani: 1-e-2-e · 4/4</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
 
<!-- ================================================================
     MÓDULO 10 — PRIMEIRA MÚSICA COMPLETA
================================================================ -->
<div class="section" id="sec10">
 
  <div class="mod-header">
    <div class="mod-num" style="background:var(--rose)">10</div>
    <div class="mod-meta">
      <div class="mod-tag" style="color:var(--rose)">Módulo 10 · Música</div>
      <div class="mod-title">Minha Primeira Música Completa!</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="mod-desc">Chegou a hora! Vamos aprender uma melodia inteira — passo a passo, com o método de Gramani e as sílabas do Konnakol. Cada frase tem sua cor, seu ritmo e sua sílaba.</p>
 
  <!-- Progress steps -->
  <div class="card" style="padding:20px;">
    <h3 style="margin-bottom:16px;">📋 Etapas de Aprendizado</h3>
    <div class="steps" id="learn-steps">
      <div class="step done" onclick="setLearnStep(0)">
        <div class="step-n">1</div>
        <div class="step-label">Sinta o Pulso</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step" onclick="setLearnStep(1)">
        <div class="step-n">2</div>
        <div class="step-label">Fale as Sílabas</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step" onclick="setLearnStep(2)">
        <div class="step-n">3</div>
        <div class="step-label">Cante a Melodia</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step" onclick="setLearnStep(3)">
        <div class="step-n">4</div>
        <div class="step-label">Dedilhe as Notas</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step" onclick="setLearnStep(4)">
        <div class="step-n">5</div>
        <div class="step-label">Toque Completo!</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="step-hint" style="font-size:13px;color:var(--ink2);background:var(--parchment);border-radius:12px;padding:12px 16px;font-weight:600;"></div>
  </div>
 
  <!-- Música: Escadinha do Ré (original para aula) -->
  <div class="card">
    <h3>🎵 "Escadinha do Ré" — Melodia Original para Aula</h3>
    <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--ink3);margin-bottom:16px;font-weight:600;">Compasso 4/4 · Andamento ♩=72 · Tonalidade: Ré maior</p>
 
    <!-- Frase 1 -->
    <div style="margin-bottom:6px;font-size:11px;font-weight:800;color:var(--ink3);letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;">Frase 1 — Subida</div>
    <div class="song-row">
      <div class="rblock" style="border-color:var(--gold);background:var(--gold-lt);">
        <div class="rb-note" style="color:var(--gold);">Ré</div><div class="rb-syl">Ta</div>
      </div>
      <div class="rblock" style="border-color:var(--plum);background:var(--plum-lt);">
